 `TOOLS.md` | Updated | Enhanced search_logic with parallel_execution config |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 วิธีใช้งาน (สำหรับ Journey Architect)\n\n```typescript\n// ใน Orchestrator หรือ Journey Architect\nimport { parallelSearch, searchHighlightsOnly } from './pinecone-config';\n\n// 1. ค้นหาแบบ Parallel (ได้ทั้ง text และ video)\nconst results = await parallelSearch(userQuery, embedding, 3);\n\n// 2. ตรวจสอบผลลัพธ์\nif (results.video_results.length > 0) {\n  // ส่งต่อให้ 3-Filter System ตัดสินใจ\n  // Filter 3: Interest Match -> ส่ง video ทันที\n}\n\n// 3. ค้นหาเฉพาะ Highlights (สำหรับ Filter 3)\nconst highlights = await searchHighlightsOnly(embedding, 0.7, 3);\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 Technical Notes\n\n- **Pinecone Index:** `aunjai-knowledge`\n- **Namespace:** `highlights`\n- **Min Score:** 0.70 (สำหรับ video recommendations)\n- **Top K:** 3-5 results ต่อแหล่งข้อมูล\n- **Parallel Execution:** ใช้ Promise.all() เพื่อความเร็ว\n\n---\n\n*Logged by: System Tuner Agent*  \n*Date: 2026-03-11*  \n*Reference: Search Specialist Parallel Search Implementation*\n","file_path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-unjai/memory/2026-03-11.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":408,"output":1059,"cacheRead":92672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94139,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773225171232}}
