er 1: Content Depth\n    is_fact_check = check_keywords([\"ข้อ\", \"บท\", \"อ้างอิง\"])\n    is_emotional = check_keywords([\"เศร้า\", \"เหนื่อย\", \"ท้อ\"])\n    \n    # Filter 2: R-Score Threshold\n    if r_score < 30: return \"text_only\"\n    elif 30 <= r_score < 60 and has_highlights: return \"video_nudge\"\n    elif r_score >= 60 and has_highlights: return \"video_package\"\n    \n    # Filter 3: Interest Match (มี video ตรงกับคำถาม)\n    return \"text_only\"\n```\n\n**Response Types:**\n- `text_only` - ตอบข้อความธรรมดา\n- `video_nudge` - แนะนำวิดีโอเบาๆ (Circle 1-2)\n- `video_package` - วิดีโอ + Quiz (Circle 2+)\n\n#### 4. Flex Message Builder\n\n**Video Card:**\n- Thumbnail from YouTube\n- Title + Description\n- Tags\n- \"▶ ดูวิดีโอ\" button\n\n**Quiz Card:**\n- Question header\n- Multiple choice buttons\n- Postback actions\n\n---\n\n## 📁 Files Modified/Created\n\n| File | Action | Details |\n|------|--------|---------|\n| `modules/line_orchestrator.py` | **NEW** | Complete integration layer |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 วิธีใช้งานใน Production\n\n### 1. Environment Variables (ต้องมี)\n```bash\n# Pinecone\nPINECONE_API_KEY=pcsk_ue4k1_...\nPINECONE_INDEX_NAME=aunjai-knowledge\nPINECONE_NAMESPACE=highlights\nPINECONE_INDEX_HOST=https://aunjai-knowledge-3ygam8j.svc.aped-4627-b74a.pinecone.io\n\n# OpenAI (สำหรับ embeddings)\nOPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...\n\n# LINE\nLINE_CHANNEL_ACCESS_TOKEN=...\nLINE_CHANNEL_SECRET=...\n\n# Redis\nREDIS_HOST=localhost\nREDIS_PORT=6379\n```\n\n### 2. เรียกใช้งานใน FastAPI\n\n```python\nfrom modules.line_orchestrator import line_orchestrator\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI, Request\n\napp = FastAPI()\n\n@app.post(\"/webhook\")\nasync def webhook(request: Request):\n    # LineOrchestrator จัดการทั้งหมด\n    return await line_orchestrator.line_gateway.handle_webhook(request)\n```\n\n### 3. Flow การทำงานจริง\n\n```\nUser sends message on LINE\n    ↓\nLINE Gateway รับ webhook\n    ↓\nSearch Specialist → parallel_search()\n    ├── Generate embedding (OpenAI)\n    ├── Search Pinecone (vector similarity)\n    └── Return video_results[]\n    ↓\nJourney Architect → decide_response_type()\n    ├── Filter 1: Content Depth\n    ├── Filter 2: R-Score Threshold  \n    └── Filter 3: Interest Match\n    ↓\nBuild Response (Text / Video / Video+Quiz)\n    ↓\nSend back to LINE (Flex Message)\n    ↓\nUpdate Session (R-score, history)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🧪 Testing Commands\n\n```bash\n# Test Pinecone connection\ncurl -X POST https://aunjai-knowledge-.../query \\\n  -H \"Api-Key: $PINECONE_API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"namespace\": \"highlights\",\n    \"vector\": [0.1, 0.2, ...],  # 384 dimensions\n    \"topK\": 3,\n    \"includeMetadata\": true\n  }'\n```\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Important Notes\n\n1. **Embeddings:** ต้องใช้ OpenAI API key เพื่อสร้าง vector (384 dimensions)\n2. **Min Score:** 0.70 เป็นค่า threshold สำหรับส่ง video recommendations\n3. **Namespace:** ต้องระบุ \"highlights\" เพื่อค้นหาเฉพาะ video clips\n4. **Fallback:** ถ้า Pinecone ล่ม ระบบจะ fallback เป็น text-only response\n\n---\n\n*Logged by: System Tuner Agent*  \n*Date: 2026-03-11*  \n*Reference: LINE Gateway + Pinecone Integration - Production Ready*\n","file_path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-unjai/memory/2026-03-11.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":2577,"output":1811,"cacheRead":103168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107556,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773226866674}}
